  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Explode everyone as a Duck!</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as vigilante driver Ducky Hardbeak, fully loaded with automatic weapons, rocket launchers and commentary!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras/0025d287cfd21862dd99dbb80eb66b67.avif?t=1753374882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras_big/0025d287cfd21862dd99dbb80eb66b67.avif?t=1753374882 width=800 height=354 /></span><strong><u>Single Player and Multiplayer</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down and destroy anyone or anything in your way whether man, machine, or something else entirely (your friends).<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras/d22f4aa2364d582532c245d16d0b0593.avif?t=1753374882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras_big/d22f4aa2364d582532c245d16d0b0593.avif?t=1753374882 width=800 height=446 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Show a softer side?</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up chicks and upgrades to defend the roost! Playable on both PC and VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras/8233ee1b9b72956083bf06622d4ffe57.avif?t=1753374882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras_big/8233ee1b9b72956083bf06622d4ffe57.avif?t=1753374882 width=800 height=356 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Explode everyone as a Duck!</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as vigilante driver Ducky Hardbeak, fully loaded with automatic weapons, rocket launchers and commentary!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras/0025d287cfd21862dd99dbb80eb66b67.avif?t=1753374882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras_big/0025d287cfd21862dd99dbb80eb66b67.avif?t=1753374882 width=800 height=354 /></span><strong><u>Single Player and Multiplayer</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down and destroy anyone or anything in your way whether man, machine, or something else entirely (your friends).<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras/d22f4aa2364d582532c245d16d0b0593.avif?t=1753374882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras_big/d22f4aa2364d582532c245d16d0b0593.avif?t=1753374882 width=800 height=446 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Show a softer side?</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up chicks and upgrades to defend the roost! Playable on both PC and VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras/8233ee1b9b72956083bf06622d4ffe57.avif?t=1753374882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867200/extras_big/8233ee1b9b72956083bf06622d4ffe57.avif?t=1753374882 width=800 height=356 /></span></p>",
